trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support for <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone" /> controls.
trans-unit.target: Ofrece compatibilidad en tiempo de diseño para los controles <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone" />.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneDesigner> provides design-time rendering of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> controls.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneDesigner> Proporciona un procesamiento de tiempo de diseño de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> controles.

trans-unit.source: It includes support for editable designer regions, templates, and auto-formats to allow a page developer to easily alter the appearance of the control.
trans-unit.target: Incluye compatibilidad con regiones del diseñador modificables, plantillas y formatos automáticos para permitir que un desarrollador de páginas modificar fácilmente la apariencia del control.

trans-unit.source: The public <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneDesigner.AutoFormats%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> collections provide quick formatting options for the page developer and can be safely overridden to change the default appearance of a custom control.
trans-unit.target: Público <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneDesigner.AutoFormats%2A> y <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> colecciones proporcionan opciones de formato rápidos para el desarrollador de páginas y se puede invalidar para cambiar la apariencia predeterminada de un control personalizado de forma segura.

trans-unit.source: If you want to override the <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml" /> method to change the design-time appearance of your custom control, make sure to use <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml(System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection)" /> and invoke the parent method before adding custom code, because that is the method that creates the rendering for the regions in the control.
trans-unit.target: Si desea invalidar el <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml" /> método para cambiar la apariencia en tiempo de diseño del control personalizado, asegúrese de usar <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml(System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection)" /> e invocar el método principal antes de agregar código personalizado, puesto que es el método que crea la representación de la regiones en el control.

trans-unit.source: If you override <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml" /> and do not call <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml(System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection)" /> somewhere in the method, your designer regions will not be rendered.
trans-unit.target: Si invalida <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml" /> y no llame a <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml(System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection)" /> en algún lugar en el método, las regiones del diseñador no se representará.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneDesigner" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneDesigner" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of predefined automatic formatting schemes to display in the **Auto Format** dialog box for the associated control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene la colección de esquemas de formato automático predefinidos para mostrarla en tiempo de diseño en el cuadro de diálogo **Formato automático** correspondiente al control asociado.

trans-unit.source: A pre-specified <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection" /> with a default WebPartZone scheme.
trans-unit.target: Un <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection" /> especificado previamente con un esquema de WebPartZone predeterminado.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneDesigner.AutoFormats%2A> property overrides its base implementation to return a collection that is specific to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> class.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneDesigner.AutoFormats%2A> propiedad reemplaza su implementación base para devolver una colección que es específica de la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> clase.

trans-unit.source: Gets the markup that is used to represent the control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el marcado que se utiliza para representar el control en tiempo de diseño.

trans-unit.source: Gets the markup that is used to represent the control at design time by calling the <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml(System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection)" /> method with a null argument.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el marcado utilizado para representar el control en tiempo de diseño llamando al método <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml(System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection)" /> con un argumento null.

trans-unit.source: A method call to <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml(System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection)" /> with a null argument as the parameter.
trans-unit.target: Una llamada de método a <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml(System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection)" /> con un argumento null como el parámetro.

trans-unit.source: When overriding this method, you must call <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml(System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection)" /> with a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection" /> or <see langword="null" /> as an argument so that designer regions build correctly.
trans-unit.target: Al reemplazar este método, debe llamar a <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml(System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection)" /> con un <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection" /> o <see langword="null" /> como un argumento para que las regiones del diseñador se generen correctamente.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection" />, if any, associated with the control.
trans-unit.target: El objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection" />, si existe, asociado al control.

trans-unit.source: Creates an <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion" /> in the designer before generating the design-time HTML of the control.
trans-unit.target: Crea una <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion" /> en el diseñador antes de generar el HTML del control en tiempo de diseño.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> representing the design-time HTML of the control.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.String" /> que representa el HTML del control en tiempo de diseño.

trans-unit.source: When overriding this method, you must call the base method for designer regions to build correctly.
trans-unit.target: Al reemplazar este método, debe llamar al método base para las regiones del diseñador se generen correctamente.

trans-unit.source: The specified <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion" />.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion" /> especificado.

trans-unit.source: Gets the content for the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el contenido del objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion" /> especificado.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that represents the persisted form of the designer region content.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.String" /> que representa el formulario conservado del contenido de la región del diseñador.

trans-unit.source: Provides an empty string ("") if there is no design-time HTML for the associated control.
trans-unit.target: Proporciona una cadena vacía ("") si no hay ningún HTML en tiempo de diseño para el control asociado.

trans-unit.source: An empty string.
trans-unit.target: Una cadena vacía.

trans-unit.source: The associated <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone" /> control.
trans-unit.target: El control <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone" /> asociado.

trans-unit.source: Attaches the designer to the associated <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone" /> control.
trans-unit.target: Adjunta el diseñador al control <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone" /> asociado.

trans-unit.source: The specified <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion" />.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion" /> especificado.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that represents the content for the specified region.
trans-unit.target: Un objeto <see cref="T:System.String" /> que representa el contenido de la región especificada.

trans-unit.source: Sets the content of the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion" />.
trans-unit.target: Establece el contenido del objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion" /> especificado.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of template groups, each containing one or more template definitions.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene una colección de grupos de plantillas, cada una con una o varias definiciones de plantilla.

trans-unit.source: A pre-specified <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection" /> object with default settings for a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone" /> environment.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection" /> especificado previamente con una configuración predeterminada para un entorno <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> property overrides its base implementation to returns a collection that is specific to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> class.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> propiedad invalida su implementación base para devolver una colección que es específica de la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> clase.
